Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Mix cream cheese, mozzarella cheese, mayo and garlic in medium bowl until well blended. Spoon into 9-inch pie plate or casserole dish. Bake 10 min. Stir. Arrange tomatoes, artichokes and peppers over cheese mixture in 3 separate sections. Bake an additional 10 min. Serve with TRISCUITS Thin Crisps and WHEAT THIN Crackers.